    <div class="container white">
        <div class="for-background-dark col-md-5">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-12">
                <h3 class="text-center">Fight the challenges of losing weight.</h3>
                <p class="lead" >Be connected with an expert, helpful, and friendly consultant who cares about your achievement.</p>
                <h3>Process</h3>
                <p>We work with you on a one-on-one basis over Skype to consult with you on creating effective strategies to lose weight in a safe, healthy, and effective way.  We work with your schedule and take weekly satisfaction inventories to ensure we're giving you the dedicated service you deserve.</p>
                <h3>Methodology</h3>
                <p>We have used peer-reviewed science of maintaining motivation and constructing habits, losing weight and eating healthy to construct a framework for weight loss.  We work with you to customize the framework to your needs.</p>
