                <p class="lead">Get started today.  It's on us.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-12">
                <%= form_tag("/thank_you") do %>
                  <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-5">
                      <div class="form-group">
                          <%= text_field_tag :first_name, nil, class: 'form-control', placeholder: 'First Name' %>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-7">
                      <div class="form-group">
                          <%= text_field_tag :last_name, nil, class: 'form-control', placeholder: 'Last Name' %>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-12">
                      <div class="form-group">
                        <%= text_field_tag :email, nil, class: 'form-control', placeholder: 'Email Address' %>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <!--<div class="row">-->
                  <!--  <div class="col-md-12">-->
                  <!--    <div class="form-group text-area-wide">-->
                  <!--      <%# text_area_tag :message, nil, class: 'form-control text-area-wide', placeholder: 'When are you available?' %>-->
                  <!--    </div>-->
                  <!--  </div>-->
                  <!--</div>-->
                  <%= submit_tag 'Get Started', class: 'btn btn-success' %>
                  <p>We will never share or sell your personal information.  Please review our <%= link_to 'privacy policy', privacy_policy_path %>.</p>
                <% end %>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-12"><h3>Disclaimer</h3>
                  <p>Weight loss results vary per person on the following non-exhaustive list bases: height, current weight, BMI, genetic factors. Weight loss is a complicated science that no one has mastered.  For these reasons, results vary per person, and we cannot guarantee that you will lose a specific amount of weight, including, but not limited to losing weight, staying at a neutral weight, or gaining weight. </p>
              </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
